### List all users (requires auth)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/users
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### List users with pagination
GET http://localhost:3000/api/users?page=1&limit=2
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Filter users by role
GET http://localhost:3000/api/users?role=admin
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Search users
GET http://localhost:3000/api/users?search=alice
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get user by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/users/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Create new user (admin only)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/users
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "David",
  "email": "david@example.com",
  "role": "user"
}

### Update user (PUT - full replace)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/users/2
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Bob Updated",
  "email": "bob.updated@example.com",
  "role": "user"
}

### Update user (PATCH - partial)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/users/2
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Bob Patched"
}

### Delete user (admin only)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/users/3
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
